  "markup": "Every now and then you run into a case that despite your best efforts, is not responding to treatment. Every clinician has experienced this.\nYou apply all your knowledge and clinical expertise, and they\u0026rsquo;re still stuck in a holding pattern.\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nIn this webinar we will discuss these types of cases and how you can blend other techniques with your laser protocols, or simply tweak your protocols to get a breakthrough for these patients.\nJoin Dr. Chris Carraway and special guest for some clinical pearls, hints, and application tips, to help get past some roadblocks in treatment"
}]]></Value>
